lead_paragraph: Vionise Pierre-Louis had 11 of her 14 points in the fourth quarter and No. 20 Oklahoma pulled away from TCU for a 77-64 win on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Pierre-Louis Sparks No. 20 Oklahoma Women Past TCU 77-64.
